author: William
content:
William’s Den hired the Spider Mountain for our Big Camp Out / Festival weekend on 20th and 21st of July 2024. You were professional from the start providing all the relevant information needed, being on time, lovely charming staff and being a part of our event. The Spider Mountain and rock climbing wall was very popular with our guests and i would highly recommend it and DB Entertainment.
Please pass on my thanks to your staff.

William Sweeting
William’s Den
